# Optional — use when you deploy the UI (Vercel, Netlify, etc.) but the API
# runs elsewhere (Railway, Render, Fly.io, your VPS). Friends' browsers must
# talk to YOUR public API, not localhost on their PCs.
#
# No trailing slash. Example:
#   VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://meta-hackathon-api.up.railway.app
#
# After changing this file, rebuild: npm run build
VITE_BACKEND_URL=
